On Demand.name: 30 Day Tone
On Demand.description: Join Anna Victoria for a 30 day program and work out with her in real time! 30 Day Tone is based on her most popular Fit Body program, Tone. It’s perfect for beginners, anyone looking for extra guidance and accountability, or just a killer sweat sesh you can do alongside Anna.

On Demand.name: Cardio
On Demand.description: Compliment your Fit Body workouts by completing one of our cardio classes from two of our Fit Body trainers, Nicci and Brittany! These high impact classes range from 15 to 30 minutes and are designed to burn fat, get your heart rate up, and leave you feeling great.

On Demand.name: Low Impact
On Demand.description: These low impact workouts are designed to be used in connection with your Fit Body program for active recovery days or when you need low to mid intensity workouts that are easy on the joints.

On Demand.name: Yoga Flows
On Demand.description: These beginner to intermediate yoga flows can be incorporated into any Fit Body program to encourage active recovery, help improve flexibility, and lengthen and strengthen your body.

On Demand.name: Postpartum
On Demand.description: These low impact, low intensity workouts are designed for newly postpartum and post C-section mothers who need to safely strengthen their inner core muscles with exercises reviewed and approved by a Pelvic Floor Physical Therapist.

Guidance.name: Fitness
Guidance.description: Get Fit Body’s top fitness tips on everything from proper form and workout routines, to accurately tracking your progress and improving your overall performance so you can get the best results.

Guidance.name: Food
Guidance.description: Learn how to use Fit Body’s meal plans, recipes, and macro tracking along with the fundamentals of healthy eating so you can fuel your body with the nutrients it needs to feel good.

Guidance.name: Rehabilitation
Guidance.description: Watch these easy-to-follow demonstrations of repair and recovery moves that can be incorporated before, during or after any Fit Body workout.

Guidance.name: Body Love
Guidance.description: Get your mind in the right place. These lifestyle guidance videos are designed​​to help you reach your goals of achieving physical, mental, and emotional well-being through making fitness a priority while still enjoying life.
